FBIS4-50673 "drchi098_j_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-098 Daily Report 12 May 1994 Latin America & Caribbean Chilean Army Officer Meets With PLA's Li Jing Chilean Army Officer Meets With PLA's Li Jing OW1205190094 Beijing XINHUA in English 1400 GMT 12 May 94 OW1205190094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 12 (XINHUA) -- Li Jing, deputy chief of General Staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA), met with Jorge Lucar Figueroa, deputy command in chief of Chilean Army, here today. Li Laizhu, commander of the Beijing military area, was present on the occasion.
